        <abstract>
            <p>Tells of his father’s ill health.</p>
            <p>Discusses mesmerism and Harriet Martineau’s recovery. If animals could be put into a stupor, he would be convinced. Suggests WDF have some mesmeriser attempt it with cats.</p>
        </abstract>
